<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Our credit providers, Close Brothers Premium Finance, have informed us that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">your business address (provided to them when you purchased your policy) does not match that of your company's registered address</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>The registered trading address identified by Close Brothers on Companies House for your company is {ADDRESS}. </b><u style="font-weight: bold;">Please confirm if you are happy to proceed with the finance using this address</u><b><u>.</u><br></b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b><br></b>Alternatively, in order to proceed, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">if the original address is to remain unchanged, please let us know why the address provided does not match the registered or trading address of the business</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. Close Brothers will then require documentation to confirm your business name and address.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>We can accept the following documents for your business name and address as valid confirmation to be dated within the last 3 months:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Utility bill (e.g. gas, electric, water bill, not mobile);</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Bank or Building Society statement; or</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Credit card statement.</font></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Please be advised <b>without the relevant documentation, or appropriate confirmation, <u>Close Brothers will be unable to carry out the necessary due diligence for your account</u> and <u>the premium finance agreement may be cancelled</u> in the next 5 working days and <u>you will still be liable for the outstanding premium balance</u></b>.<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please contact us to discuss this on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> where we can outline your options and provide information and assistance.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>